      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_5180">
            <h1 id="director-general-chief-digital-and-information-officer">Director General, Chief Digital and Information Officer</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director General, Chief Digital and Information Officer is accountable for the strategy, maintenance, integrity, value for money and continuous improvement of Department for Work and Pensions (<abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr>) information technology (IT) services and systems.</p>

</div>
